	<tw-gaap-notes:ForeignCurrencyTransactionsAndTranslationOfForeignCurrencyFinancialStatements contextRef="From20110101To20110930"><![CDATA[　　非衍生性商品之外幣交易所產生之各項外幣資產、負債、收入
